oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Smokey Mountain Cage Bird Society OnTheMove
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Dingle, Sheldon
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The Smokey Mountain Cage BirdSociety (SMCBS) is a rather small club ofabout 70 members who live scatteredthroughout five states in and around theSouth- but the little club does bigthings.Although the club seldom has morethan 20 members present at themonthly meetings (and many of thesefo lks have to drive an hour or two eachway), it is well organized and in betterthan average contact with its membersby phone and mail. This constant communicationallows a small club to takeon some pretty awesome enterprisesand pull them off with much success.
